title: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Bulgaria Buildings, Bulgaria, 2008
name: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Bulgaria Buildings, Bulgaria, 2008
description: This data set was provided by the kind people of Open street maps. data was uploaded as a polygone file showing the boundaries of buildings in the country of Bulgaria. There are only 270 buildings, but there is great detail. this data set includes attributes for the building name if it is available.
